---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import pictureOfDylan from "/src/assets/images/croppedOnstageSolo.jpg";
---

<section
  id="About"
  class="flex flex-col items-center w-[90vw] gap-4 py-10 xl:py-20"
>
  <h2
    class="py-4 text-2xl lg:text-4xl text-center drop-shadow-2xl z-10 font-alameda tracking-wide"
  >
    About
  </h2>

  <div class="flex flex-col xl:flex-row gap-4 xl:gap-8">
    <Image
      src={pictureOfDylan}
      alt="Dylan Cole performing a guitar solo at a live show."
      widths={[]}
      sizes={``}
    />
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 max-w-xl">
      <p>
        Meet Dylan Cole, Atlanta's own country music sensation. With a guitar in
        hand and a voice that echoes the soul of the South, Dylan delivers
        electrifying solo performances that leave audiences spellbound.
      </p>
      <p>
        With a relaxed confidence, Dylan delivers performances that are both
        engaging and heartfelt, embodying the spirit of country music in a way
        that feels both familiar and refreshingly new. His music exudes a subtle
        charm, capturing the essence of what it means to navigate the
        complexities of the human experience with grace and a touch of
        seduction. Dylan Cole stands out as an artist with a deep appreciation
        for the genre's traditions, yet bold enough to infuse his work with his
        own unique flair, making his music not just heard, but felt.
      </p>
      <span
        >Ready to be swept away by Dylan Cole's performance? Secure your tickets
        now below and experience the magic firsthand.</span
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
